<content title="New Believer's Ministry">
	<ministry id="newbelievers">
	  <name>New Believer's Ministry</name>
	  <overview>The purpose of the New Believer's Ministry is to make disciples by
                teaching students to observe all things Jesus has commanded us.
                </overview>
	  <long-description>
        <p>
        Want to grow in your understanding of basic Bible teachings?  Either for the
        first time or to refresh your understanding of these fundamental truths?  Then a
        New Believer's class may be just for you.  
        The New Believer's classes are opportunities for other like minded individuals and
        provide an opportunity for fellowship with one another.
        </p>
        <p>
        These 12-week classes are offered at
        various times through out the year and are available for adults seeking to grow
        in this way.
        Students in advance of class night spend
        time in praying for one another and studying the Bible using curriculum provided
        by the instructor.
        The <link href="http://www.calvarychapel.com/costamesa/newbelievers/study/index.htm">New Believer's curriculum</link> is based 
        on materials provided by Calvary Chapel Costa Mesa.
	    </p>
	  </long-description>
	  <contacts>
        <contact-email email="craig.swearingen@netzero.net">Craig Swearingen</contact-email>
   	  </contacts>
	</ministry>
</content>
